    >[ ] learn to export things to VTODO format $Plans done (commit 4ad774c/43b6e07): plan_to_event -> plan_to_todo, parse_ics_file reads VEVENT+VTODO both. Action-mirror half (action_to_vevent -> action_to_vtodo) deliberately NOT done yet - it shares parse_ics_file/read_ics_dates with reconcile's 3-way sync, so it must land together with reconcile becoming VTODO-aware and a migration path for existing action mirrors, not piecemeal. See caldav-integration/README.md design notes 2026-07-12.$ #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3a974ca12f85
    >[ ] read apply_sync's write ordering/locking before touching action-mirror sync $Prerequisite for the action-mirror VTODO swap (learn to import VTODO). apply_sync's doc comment says ordering is load-bearing - TakeAction/TakeCalendar/Converged each stage .actions + sidecar writes differently via PendingBatch. Need to actually trace this before changing what read_ics_dates reads, since a mis-sequenced change here can silently clear a real scheduled_at (mistaking 'can't find the old format' for 'calendar deleted the event'). See caldav-integration/README.md design notes 2026-07-12.$ #019f5a22-7252-7c22-8e66-96aae8692720
    >[ ] learn to import VTODO $Bigger than the name implies: action_to_vevent -> action_to_vtodo, read_ics_dates/reconcile made VTODO-aware, AND a migration command for existing action-mirror .ics files - these three must land together as one atomic change, not piecemeal, because read_ics_dates/parse_ics_file is shared between plan parsing and the action-mirror 3-way reconcile. Depends on the apply_sync ordering review (previous action). See caldav-integration/README.md design notes 2026-07-12.$ #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3abe216ea948
    >[ ] add fields to the sync list of the sidecar ~ $Genericize reconcile() to reconcile<T: PartialEq + Clone> and add a _sync merge-base column per field (state, title, description, due_date), same shape as scheduled_at_sync. due_date_sync already exists on Action/ActionMeta but is unused by any reconcile call; state_sync/title_sync/description_sync are net-new. See caldav-integration/README.md design notes 2026-07-12.$ #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3adcba9847ba
